{"tid":1903192,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"無聊得滯 改咗中共一首歌","createTime":"2020-02-28T20:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T09:42:28.000Z","uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d46589c86e286592e1442bc592137d463251ba9","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:19:19.000Z","msg":"本來po喺音樂台，但係冇人理所以喺呢度再po多次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東方紅， 光照天， 天下出左一個當勞侵。<br />\n佢為天下謀興旺， Hallelujah， 救港自由大恩人。<br />\n當勞侵，愛香港， 佢係我哋嘅領羊人。<br />\n捍衛自由護香港， Hallelujah，帶領我哋照光芒<br />\n當勞侵，似陽光，照到邊度邊度光。 邊度地方有光照， Hallelujah， 嗰邊地方得光榮。<br />\n<br />\n唔好問我邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不喜勿歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無聊得滯 改咗中共一首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f46c40fb50dfb556834b786959a65b6d4bc003a0","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:19:42.000Z","msg":"pish 1"},{"pid":"71422edba886aa39077cd35b1e7b2cbbfc6b6d2e","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:19:52.000Z","msg":"pish 2"},{"pid":"d719f7068a7a544be5a2fe69048297b0de2c4ecf","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:20:23.000Z","msg":"pish 3"},{"pid":"0f69f6e929a4c74628d9e9e895afd238d9519293","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:20:33.000Z","msg":"pish 4"},{"pid":"fe91645400f8a37ad32e72a1ffb25028819043c0","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:21:35.000Z","msg":"pish 5"},{"pid":"798839327a551a85356a272b0c8c73bb3983261d","tid":1903192,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T20:22:54.000Z","msg":"pish 6"},{"pid":"e5266547aacebb002bcf2c68695d4